      • getCardTypeFromJson

        public CardType getCardTypeFromJson(org.json.JSONObject jsonObject)
        Parses out the card type from the json and returns a CardType. If the type is that of a CardType.SHORT_NEWS and no image url is present, then the type returned will be that of a CardType.TEXT_ANNOUNCEMENT.
        Parameters:
        jsonObject - The json object of the Card.
        Returns:
        The CardType if parsable from the json or CardType.DEFAULT.

      • getServerKeyFromCardType

        public java.lang.String getServerKeyFromCardType(CardType cardType)
        Returns the server key for the CardType, or null if the server key cannot be found.
